    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.anthropic.com/v1/messages",
        "sendHeaders": true,
        "headerParameters": {
          "parameters": [
            {
              "name": "x-api-key",
              "value": "YOUR_ANTHROPIC_API_KEY"
            },
            {
              "name": "anthropic-version",
              "value": "2023-06-01"
            },
            {
              "name": "Content-Type",
              "value": "application/json"
            }
          ]
        },
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={{\n  {\n    model: \"claude-sonnet-4-6\",\n    max_tokens: 1200,\n    messages: [\n      {\n        role: \"user\",\n        content:\n          \"Based on this research:\\n\\n\" +\n          $json.choices[0].message.content +\n          `\n\nReturn exactly one valid raw JSON object using exactly these keys:\n\n{\n  \"company_name\": \"plain text string\",\n  \"aos\": \"plain text string\",\n  \"link\": \"plain text string\",\n  \"news_and_leverage\": \"plain text string\"\n}\n\nStrict rules:\n- Use exactly these four keys and no others.\n- Every value must be a plain string.\n- Do not return nested objects.\n- Do not return arrays.\n- Do not use markdown.\n- Do not use code fences.\n- Do not include any text before or after the JSON.\n- If information is unavailable, use an empty string.\n`\n      }\n    ]\n  }\n}}",
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.4,
      "position": [
        1216,
        0
      ],
      "id": "b844ee0d-c519-4e14-a396-7e023c032144",
      "name": "HTTP Request2"
